name: HTMLEmbedElement
description: The HTMLEmbedElement interface, which provides special properties (beyond the regular HTMLElement interface it also has available to it by inheritance) for manipulating <embed> elements.

members.name: HTMLEmbedElement.align
members.description: Is a DOMString representing an enumerated property indicating alignment of the element's contents with respect to the surrounding context. The possible values are "left", "right", "center", and "justify".

members.name: HTMLEmbedElement.height
members.description: Is a DOMString reflecting the height HTML attribute, containing the displayed height of the resource.

members.name: HTMLEmbedElement.name
members.description: Is a DOMString representing the name of the embedded object.

members.name: HTMLEmbedElement.src
members.description: Is a DOMString that reflects the src HTML attribute, containing the address of the resource.

members.name: HTMLEmbedElement.type
members.description: Is a DOMString that reflects the type HTML attribute, containing the type of the resource.

members.name: HTMLEmbedElement.width
members.description: Is a DOMString that reflects the width HTML attribute, containing the displayed width of the resource.
